4214,'','Fetching all tags (+ workaround)\nHi,\r\n\r\nI want to fetch a list of all used (!) tags.\r\nPreviously (0.4.2) I used the following code:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar when = require(\'when\');\r\n\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n    /**\r\n     * Returns a promise to get all tags\r\n     *\r\n     * @returns {Promise}\r\n     */\r\n    getAllTags: function ()\r\n    {\r\n        // need to lazy-loaded, because it is initially not yet initialized\r\n        var api = require("../core/server/api");\r\n\r\n        return api.posts.browse({limit: 100000}).then(\r\n            function (postModel)\r\n            {\r\n                var tags = {};\r\n                var posts = postModel.posts;\r\n\r\n                for (var i = 0, l = posts.length; i < l; i++)\r\n                {\r\n                    var post = posts[i];\r\n\r\n                    for (var j = 0, m = post.tags.length; j < m; j++)\r\n                    {\r\n                        var tag = post.tags[j];\r\n                        tags[ tag.id ] = tag;\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n\r\n                return tags;\r\n            }\r\n        );\r\n    }\r\n};\r\n```\r\n\r\nNot very efficient, but worked reasonably well (and I have found no other way).\r\n\r\nThis doesn\'t work in 0.5.2 anymore, because now I only get the tag ids in `post.tags` and not the complete tag object anymore.\r\n\r\nWhat do I need to change?\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nI tried to mitigate this issue by loading all tags with `api.tags.browse({})` and merge them manually.\r\n\r\nCuriously enough I get a "no permission error"\r\n```\r\nPossibly unhandled Error\r\n    at Error.NoPermissionError (/core/server/errors/no-permission-error.js:6:18)\r\n    at /core/server/api/tags.js:26:35\r\n    at tryCatch1 (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/util.js:43:21)\r\n    at Promise$_callHandler [as _callHandler] (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/promise.js:649:13)\r\n    at Promise$_settlePromiseFromHandler [as _settlePromiseFromHandler] (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/promise.js:663:18)\r\n    at Promise$_settlePromiseAt [as _settlePromiseAt] (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/promise.js:826:14)\r\n    at Promise$_settlePromises [as _settlePromises] (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/promise.js:960:14)\r\n    at Promise$_rejectPromises [as _rejectPromises] (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/promise.js:953:10)\r\n    at Async$_consumeFunctionBuffer [as _consumeFunctionBuffer] (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/async.js:75:12)\r\n    at Async$consumeFunctionBuffer (/node_modules/bluebird/js/main/async.js:38:14)\r\n```'
