3847,'',"Exporter: Fix and accept posts with old UUID\nCloses #3844\r\n- If a post has an old UUID format (eg\r\n'52825818238f7'), we'll create a new UUID using uuid.v4() and the\r\ncreation timestamp as basis.\r\n- Test not included. Reason: UUID validation is omnipresent,\r\ncreating/importing/editing a post to hold a wrong UUID therefore\r\nimpossible. In order to write a test, we’d have to overwrite APIs,\r\nwhich seems excessive."
