3811,'',"Post settings menu static page checkbox not sending request on editor\nIn the process of moving to GUI-2.0, where the PSM only exists on the editor, it has become apparent that the static page checkbox in the PSM menu on the editor screen doesn't do anything until the save button is pressed.\r\n\r\nThe togglePage action doesn't get called, so the model isn't saved and no request fires.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. open an existing post for editing\r\n2. open the console\r\n3. open the post settings menu, and click the static page checkbox\r\n4. notice no ajax request is fired\r\n5. try to leave the editor and the unsaved changes warning will appear\r\n\r\n### Technical details: \r\n\r\n* Ghost Version: 0.5"
3810,'','Post-GUI-Update Changes\nAs a part of the new GUI update - we are introducing many brand new (shiny!) bugs! This issue is intended to cover the things that need some additional TLC\r\n\r\n- [x] Ember body classes - #3792 - This should make the mobile nav menu on the /ghost/settings work\r\n- [x] New Ember love to handle transitioning between settings views on mobile\r\n- [x] New Ember love on new mobile menu, @PaulAdamDavis did a first implementation of this here, which needs porting in: https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost-UI/blob/GUI-2.0/docs/js/nav.js\r\n- [x] CSS bug, fix vertical centering on 404 page\r\n- [x] CSS bug, User profile settings needs to be unfucked <= @Johnonolan to provide mockup for how\r\n- [x] The markdown tab is borked - #3813\r\n- [x] Fix the Edit User UI cog icon / menu and back button #3925 \r\n- [x] Regression: Lost settings nav icons\r\n- [x] Ember redux on the "back" button switching between mobile views on /ghost/content #4031\r\n- [x] Remove animated page transitions from mobile settings\r\n\r\nLet\'s keep all New-GUI related bugs in the list above. Discussion below. Check em off as you go.\r\n\r\nFucking poetry.'
