3156,'','Line breaks not inserted on home page\n### Issue Summary\r\n\r\nWhen creating a post with line breaks, they are not displayed on the homepage (the post is cut off with an ellipsis).\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Create a post with the following text\r\n\r\n    This is a bug\r\n    \r\n    New lines rock!\r\n    \r\n    Ghost is awesome :-)\r\n\r\n2. Visit the homepage and see the following\r\n\r\n    This is a bug New lines rock! Ghost is awesome :-)\r\n\r\nThis is a bug, as all three lines are displayed as one on the home page.\r\n\r\n### Technical details\r\n\r\n* Ghost Version: 0.4\r\n* Client OS:  Windows\r\n* Browser: Internet Explorer'
