3141,'','Casper Not Installing w/ Current "Install Ghost for Developers" guide\n## Issue Summary\r\n\r\nWhen following the following four steps from the guide,\r\n\r\n>1. npm install -g grunt-cli\r\n>2. npm install\r\n>3. grunt init (and grunt prod if you want to run Ghost in production mode)\r\n>4. npm start\r\n\r\ncasper doesn\'t get initialized, so you\'ll see the following error upon npm start.\r\n\r\n>Warning: Found a theme with no package.json file\r\n> Theme name: casper\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Reproduction Steps\r\n\r\n1. Clone the ghost repo\r\n2. Follow the [getting started guide for developers](https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost#getting-started-guide-for-developers)\r\n3. You\'ll see this\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1207005/3414997/dbdf48b6-fe1b-11e3-82f9-950c90684700.png)\r\n\r\n## Specs\r\n\r\nCommit: master, `0436fb71d25d49e6a3`\r\nOS: Win8\r\nHigh fives: Given freely'
