3069,'',"Regression: Have to click 2 times to load posts on mobile\nFirst click runs the network activity - 2nd click does the animation transition. LiceCAP sadly cropped out the NProgress bar. \r\n\r\nWhat's happening is:\r\n\r\n1. I click\r\n2. NProgress loads\r\n3. I click again\r\n4. The panel slides\r\n5. repeat\r\n\r\n![lolwut](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/120485/3371782/eab76d2e-fba4-11e3-9249-4d62bfd23a08.gif)\r\n"
