2943,'','[Ember.js] Transition user to original URL after SignIn\nSignIn needs to check if the user was heading somewhere besides `/ghost/ember/` and route them appropriate after a signin.\r\n\r\nIf a user is not signed in and goes to `/ghost/ember/editor/2` or any other particular URL, ember will redirect them to `/ghost/ember/signin` and lose the state of where it was they **actually** were going. \r\n'
