2921,'',"Ember inpsector error\nWhile working on #2547 i noticed that in the Ember Inspector, when i'm in the View Tree for the upload.model view and i click on the 'model', which in this case is a user model object,  i get a JS error in the console.\r\n\r\nerror is happening here:\r\nhttps://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/blob/master/core/client/models/user.js#L44\r\n\r\nPR coming to make sure it first checks that a website value first exists"
