2918,'','[Ember.js] Bug:: Editor Save Button can\'t unpublish\n## Issue Summary\r\n\r\nThe Editor save button is broken on master :/\r\n\r\n## Repro Steps\r\n\r\n1. Open a published post in the editor\r\n2. Click on the little up arrow that lets you changes what the save button does, and click on "Unpublish"\r\n3. Be sad, because that did nothing :/\r\n\r\n## Tech specs\r\n\r\nWindows 8, Master `4406d350c43d6899dad088c2bba`\r\n'
