2861,'','[Ember.js] Update CSRF without refreshing\nThere are certain cases in the new Ember admin app (such as #2842) where the current CSRF is invalidated and a new one is needed to successfully complete future requests.\r\n\r\nCurrently, the only work around is to refresh the page, but that is undesirable. \r\n\r\nThis issue is to implement something that will allow for updating the CSRF set on the client with out the need to ever refresh the page / reload the entire application.'
