2840,'','Added popover component\nCloses #2418, #2714\r\nRef #2446, #2565\r\n\r\n- Added and injected `popover` service to globally control popovers\r\n- Added `gh-popover-button` component\r\n- Added `popover-mixin` for popover and popover-buttons to mixin\r\n- Added `body-event-listener` mixin for popover service to watch for body\r\n  clicks with\r\n- Post settings and post save button both now use `gh-popover`\r\n- Added hacks to `ember-hacks.css` to make popovers work until ghost-ui\r\n  consolidates functionality\r\n\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n**Notes on using the popover component:**\r\n\r\nPopovers work by using two separate components, the `{{gh-popover}}` itself and a `{{gh-popover-button}}` which does the actual toggling.\r\n\r\nEach `gh-popover` and `gh-popover-button` pair are connected 1-1 via a `popoverName` property (or just `name` for the popover.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n```html\r\n{{#gh-popover-button popoverName="someUniqueName" ...}}\r\n.....\r\n{{/gh-popover-button}}\r\n\r\n...\r\n\r\n{{#gh-popover name="someUniqueName" ...}}\r\n...\r\n{{/gh-popover}}\r\n```\r\n* The button and popover do not need to be anywhere near each other in the html.\r\n* By default, popovers do not close when they (and their content) are clicked on. If that behavior is desired, you can set its `closeOnClick` property to `"true"`.\r\n* Popovers fade in via the fade-in class. They do not fade out.\r\n* Ghost UI needs updating to work with these cats (@pauladamdavis). Right now, they have the class `ghost-popover`, and their display is toggled via an ember-applied `open` class. For now, `ember-hacks.css` is making it work  `ghost-ui.css` by arguing over a few particular selectors.\r\n* Speaking of Ghost UI, by default the `gh-popover-button` uses the `<button>` tag, but a few of these buttons had to be `<a>` tags due to Ghost UI\'s css. Ref: [here](https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/pull/2840/files#diff-7ba4fa206ff25814a0a663fd93cdac66R12), [here](https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/pull/2840/files#diff-2d7c6b924223211ccc4d16b09ccbd4afR17) and [here](https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/pull/2840/files#diff-b5089ba3437f07fd940d428c667a2791R17)\r\n'
