2779,'',"[Ember.js] Admin auth redirects\nAt the moment the admin authentication redirects that we have in `/server/routes/admin.js` and `server/middleware/middleware.js` don't apply to the Ember admin.\r\n\r\nThese are the redirects like redirecting signin -> ghost if the user is logged in, and redirecting signin -> signup if there is no user yet.\r\n\r\nWhilst the ember admin lives at `/ghost/ember/` this is going to involve a bit of hacky duplication, but I think it will be useful to add so that we can see the full extent of what is and isn't working."
