2628,'',"New `/view/` route for posts in editor\nIn Ghost 0.4.1 we introduced a magic `/edit/` route for the frontend. Add `/edit` to the end of any post URL, and it will take you to the editor screen for that post.\r\n\r\nWe would like to add the opposite route, where adding `/view/` to the end of the URL when you're viewing a post in the editor will take you the post on the frontend of the blog, so if I'm at `/ghost/editor/1/` and I change the URL to `/ghost/editor/1/view` I'll be taken to `/welcome-to-ghost/` or the date version of that permalink if date permalinks are enabled.\r\n\r\nThis route will probably eventually have a button somewhere on the editor, but for now we should only add the route."
