2557,'','[Build Failure] Image drop zone modal renders correctly\nI have troubles running our test suite on a new computer. I get the following error in approximately 3 out of 5 test runs. I think this failure is a timing issue with sending two `PUT` requests when saving cover image and blog logo. I\'ll send a PR to remove the second `PUT` request.\r\n\r\n```\r\nFAIL Image drop zone modal renders correctly\r\n#    type: assertExists\r\n#    file: /home/vagrant/code/Ghost/core/test/functional/admin/settings_test.js:164\r\n#    code: test.assertExists(\'.js-drop-zone.image-uploader\', \'Image drop zone modal renders correctly\');\r\n#    subject: false\r\n#    selector: ".js-drop-zone.image-uploader"\r\n⚠\xa0\xa0looks you did not use begin() which is mandatory since 1.1\r\nFAIL AssertionError: Image drop zone modal renders correctly\r\n#    type: error\r\n#    file: /home/vagrant/code/Ghost/core/test/functional/admin/settings_test.js\r\n#    subject: false\r\n#    error: {"message":"Image drop zone modal renders correctly","name":"AssertionError","result":{"success":false,"type":"assertExists","standard":"Found an element matching: .js-drop-zone.image-uploader","message":"Image drop zone modal renders correctly","file":"/home/vagrant/code/Ghost/core/test/functional/admin/settings_test.js","doThrow":true,"values":{"subject":false,"selector":".js-drop-zone.image-uploader"},"line":164,"lineContents":"test.assertExists(\'.js-drop-zone.image-uploader\', \'Image drop zone modal renders correctly\');","suite":"Ensure image upload modals display correctly","time":153},"line":301,"sourceId":140441123959232,"sourceURL":"/home/vagrant/casperjs/modules/tester.js","stack":"AssertionError: Image drop zone modal renders correctly\\n    at assert (/home/vagrant/casperjs/modules/tester.js:301)\\n    at assertExists (/home/vagrant/casperjs/modules/tester.js:493)\\n    at assertImageUploaderModalThenClose (/home/vagrant/code/Ghost/core/test/functional/admin/settings_test.js:164)\\n    a