2390,'','Intermittent (sorry) exception in core/server/helpers/index.js: "TypeError: Cannot read property \'title\' of undefined"\nOn our production blog (Ghost 0.4 from the DigitalOcean image) we\'re getting unhandled exceptions as below every 5 minutes or so. I\'m doing my best to make it reproducible but at the moment it just fails doing the same GET that has succeeded many times previously.\r\n\r\n```\r\n/var/www/ghost/core/server/helpers/index.js:396\r\n            title = this.post.title;\r\n                             ^\r\nTypeError: Cannot read property \'title\' of undefined\r\n    at Object.coreHelpers.meta_title (/var/www/ghost/core/server/helpers/index.js:396:30)\r\n    at Object.<anonymous> (/var/www/ghost/core/server/helpers/index.js:588:25)\r\n    at Function.Waiter.resolve (/var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/async.js:80:3)\r\n    at Object.<anonymous> (/var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/hbs.js:393:18)\r\n    at Object.eval (eval at <anonymous> (/var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/compiler/javascript-compiler.js:179:23), <anonymous>:20:54)\r\n    at /var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/runtime.js:92:31\r\n    at /var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/compiler/compiler.js:467:21\r\n    at /var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/hbs.js:279:26\r\n    at Function.Waiter.done (/var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/async.js:60:12)\r\n    at render (/var/www/ghost/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/hbs.js:269:11)\r\n```\r\n\r\nI\'ll update this as I find more information.'
