2302,'','Importer breaks on post status\nI tried importing my wordpress content and got the following error: "... Status cannot be null...."\r\n\r\nI looked in my json and found one entry with "Status:null". After I changed it to draft the import works. \r\nAs it turnes out this post was marked as private in wordpress.\r\n\r\nBelow the entry:\r\n```JSON\r\n{\r\n\t"id":447,\r\n\t"title":"[POST] Post-Topics",\r\n\t"slug":"post-topics",\r\n\t"markdown":".....",\r\n\t"image":null,\r\n\t"featured":0,\r\n\t"page":0,\r\n\t"status":null,\r\n\t"language":"en_US",\r\n\t"meta_title":null,\r\n\t"meta_description":null,\r\n\t"author_id":1,\r\n\t"created_at":"Tue, 13 Dec 2011 18:54:38 +0000",\r\n\t"created_by":1,\r\n\t"updated_at":"Wed, 22 Aug 2012 20:06:10 +0000",\r\n\t"updated_by":1,\r\n\t"published_at":"Tue, 13 Dec 2011 18:54:38 +0000",\r\n\t"published_by":1\r\n}\r\n```'
