2287,'','Keep apps UI behind a config option\nWith the thought in mind that we may need or want to ship a 0.4.2 at any time, and that the app UI is going to be incomplete for some time, I think it may be a good idea to only show the app UI and anything related to it if a config option is set: `apps: true` or something similar?\r\n\r\nThis will allow us to continue to develop it with confidence that users are not cloning the latest master and having a shock!'
