2012,'',"Origin 'https://www.kickstarter.com' is not allowed access.\n### Issue Summary\r\n\r\nIf you play the intro video on homepage then you see the below error in Chrome's console.\r\n\r\nXMLHttpRequest cannot load http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/johnonolan/ghost-just-a-blogging-platform/video/plays. No 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' header is present on the requested resource. Origin 'https://www.kickstarter.com' is therefore not allowed access.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Open Chrome\r\n2. Open https://ghost.org/features/\r\n3. Click on Play video button which is near Getting Started with Ghost"
