2009,'','Can\'t load custom partial in Ghost 0.4.0\nHi, I know I\'ve reported this problem before, and that it seems to have been fixed when I run my theme in development (mac os x) but in production on an Ubuntu box it crashes with this error:\r\n\r\n```\r\n/usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/runtime.js:135\r\n    throw new Exception("The partial " + name + " could not be found");\r\n          ^\r\nError: The partial socialmedia could not be found\r\n    at new Error (<anonymous>)\r\n    at Error.Exception (/usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/exception.js:6:41)\r\n    at Object.invokePartial (/usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/runtime.js:135:11)\r\n    at Object.invokePartialWrapper [as invokePartial] (/usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/runtime.js:38:34)\r\n    at Object.eval (eval at <anonymous> (/usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/compiler/javascript-compiler.js:179:23), <anonymous>:82:17)\r\n    at /usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/runtime.js:92:31\r\n    at /usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/node_modules/handlebars/dist/cjs/handlebars/compiler/compiler.js:467:21\r\n    at render (/usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/hbs.js:268:15)\r\n    at renderIt (/usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/hbs.js:323:18)\r\n    at /usr/share/nginx/www/ghost-0.4.0/node_modules/express-hbs/lib/hbs.js:329:11\r\nerror: Forever detected script exited with code: 8\r\nerror: Forever restarting script for 4 time\r\n```'
2008,'hswolff','[Docs] Documentation regarding Ghost as an NPM module\nI am excited that the newest version of Ghost supports its usage as an NPM module. However, I could not figure out how to use it properly, specifically how to create custom routes to new pages (ex: about, contact, etc)'
2006,'',"Random 500 Internal Server Error when saving\nI'm on 0.4 and I randomly get a `500 Internal Server Error` when saving or updating a post. The AJAX response is `The page cannot be displayed because an internal server error has occurred.`\r\n\r\nI get that error probably in 1 out of 10 saves and it just randomly comes up. I usually just try again and it works. \r\n\r\nI thought I'd bring it up. Thanks."
2005,'','One repository for all open-sourced Ghost themes\nTo help compile a list of open source Ghost themes, I created a [repo](https://github.com/roycehaynes/ghost-themes)  that serves as a one-stop shop for open source themes after being viewed on the marketplace. \r\n\r\nLet me know if this could be useful. @ErisDS \r\n\r\nThank you guys for kicking off Ghost. I look forward to contributing code to 0.4.1 and greater.'
