1923,'','Bug: Multiple underscores in fenced code block\n### Issue Summary\r\nMore than two underscores in a word get escaped in fenced code blocks, normal code (single backticks) work fine.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nOpen a random article and enter:\r\n\r\n    ```\r\n    a_b_c\r\n    ```\r\n\r\nThis becomes `a\\_b\\_c` but should be `a_b_c`. It works normally here on Github.\r\n\r\nUpdate: Using four spaces instead of the fenced syntax works fine.'
