1916,'','Version 0.4-pre3 - Testing\nThere is now a second pre-release of 0.4, called [0.4-pre3](https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/releases/tag/0.4.0-pre3), which has been published ready for testing.\r\n\r\n**Note:** Unless there are serious bugs, this version is what will ship as 0.4.0\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you are able to do some testing, please let us know what you have successfully tested by adding a comment here detailing what OS/en, dev/production mode, database etc.\r\n\r\n### Bugs\r\nIf you find any bugs, *please* raise them according to the [contributing guidelines](https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#bugs), you can use [this link](https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/issues/new?title=Bug%3A&body=%23%23%23%20Issue%20Summary%0A%0A%23%23%23%20Steps%20to%20Reproduce%0A%0A1.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20step%0A%0AThis%20is%20a%20bug%20because...%0A%0A%23%23%23%20Technical%20details%0A%0A*%20Ghost%20Version%3A%20master%20-%20latest%20commit%3A%20%20INSERT%20COMMIT%20REF%0A*%20Client%20OS%3A%20%0A*%20Server%20OS%3A%20%0A*%20Node%20Version%3A%20%0A*%20Browser%3A) to automatically create a new issue in the correct format.\r\n\r\n### What to test?\r\n\r\nSome important areas for testing:\r\n\r\n- using production environment \r\n- using MySQL\r\n- installing ghost in a subdirectory \r\n- turning on dated permalinks\r\n- trying out proxy-based ssl\r\n- theme switching, with partials\r\n- post editing, including adding tags, and modifying other settings\r\n- uploading images and importing files\r\n- **added** using the importer on /ghost/debug/\r\n\r\nThanks!'
