1823,'',"[Translations: /zh_TW] Traditional Chinese translations\nStarted translation into Traditional Chinese. Anyone's welcome to jump in.\r\n\r\n<h2>Progress</h2>\r\nReference: https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/pull/1679\r\n\r\n- [x] config.yml\r\n- [x] zh_TW/index.html\r\n\r\n<h4>Installation</h4>\r\n\r\n- [x] zh_TW/installation/deploy.md\r\n- [x] zh_TW/installation/index.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/installation/linux.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/installation/mac.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/installation/troubleshooting.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/installation/upgrading.md\r\n- [x] zh_TW/installation/windows.md\r\n\r\n<h4>Quickstart, Themes & Mail</h4>\r\n\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/quickstart/quickstart.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/mail/index.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/themes/index.md\r\n\r\n<h4>Usage</h4>\r\n\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/usage/index.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/usage/configuration.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/usage/faq.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/usage/index.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/usage/managing.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/usage/settings.md\r\n- [ ] zh_TW/usage/writing.md\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Check points</h2>\r\nReference: https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/pull/1494\r\n\r\n- [x] A folder with copies of all the docs files, correctly named with the IETF language code\r\n- [x] Every file should have the lang and any permalink settings changed\r\n- [x] Your language added to the _config.yml file\r\n- [x] At least one of the mac, windows or linux installation guides fully translated\r\n- [x] Someone from the Ghost team (probably @matthojo) will check there are no obvious issues and give a :+1: if all is OK\r\n- [x] A second person who speaks your language should also check the translations and give them a :+1: if they are happy"
