1791,'',"Bold text with underscores isn't properly rendered at the beginning of a line\nIssue Summary\r\n---------\r\nWhen writing a post, Ghost doesn't properly output bold text at the beginning of a line when using underscores.\r\n\r\n![screen shot 2013-12-29 at 9 11 17 pm](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/965436/1820610/500485f0-70f8-11e3-93ca-152ae0460add.png)\r\n\r\nThe same issue occurs when the post is published.\r\n\r\nSteps to Reproduce\r\n---------\r\n1. Create a new post.\r\n2. Type `__test__`.\r\n\r\nTechnical details\r\n-------\r\nGhost Version: master (64cf2b1b24642d9814e851a67ec610c73b526bc3)\r\nClient OS: Mac OS X 10.9.1\r\nServer OS: Mac OS X 10.9.1\r\nNode Version: 0.10.24\r\nBrowser: Chrome 31.0.1650.63"
