1588,'','Admin UX: doubleclicking the post item should open it in edit mode\nThis is a feature request.\r\n\r\nIn the admin panel, when you doubleclick the post listed in the left panel, it should be loaded for editing.\r\n\r\nReason:\r\n\r\nUsers will use the left panel for creating new posts and scrolling them, when they want to edit one, they have to go all the way to the right corner. This is bad UX.\r\n\r\nThe current edit button could stay there, but an optional double-click-to-edit feature should be added for quick and easy access to the edit mode of the post.'
