1269,'','Installation problem with sqlite3\nWhile trying to install ghost on my mac I received this error\r\n\r\n```\r\n> sqlite3@2.1.16 install /Users/PDXIII/Sites/ghost-0.3.3/node_modules/sqlite3\r\n> node build.js\r\n\r\n[sqlite3]: Checking for http://node-sqlite3.s3.amazonaws.com/Release/node_sqlite3-v2.1.a-node-v0x000C-darwin-x64.tar.gz\r\n[sqlite3]: http://node-sqlite3.s3.amazonaws.com/Release/node_sqlite3-v2.1.a-node-v0x000C-darwin-x64.tar.gz not found, falling back to source compile (Error: Server returned 404)\r\n  ACTION deps_sqlite3_gyp_action_before_build_target_unpack_sqlite_dep Release/obj/gen/sqlite-autoconf-3071700/sqlite3.c\r\n  TOUCH Release/obj.target/deps/action_before_build.stamp\r\n  CC(target) Release/obj.target/sqlite3/gen/sqlite-autoconf-3071700/sqlite3.o\r\n  LIBTOOL-STATIC Release/sqlite3.a\r\n  CXX(target) Release/obj.target/node_sqlite3/src/database.o\r\nBuild failed\r\n[sqlite3]: 1\r\nnpm ERR! weird error 1\r\nnpm ERR! not ok code 0\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'
