1234,'','Styling issue when browser resized.\nThere is styling issue when browser is resized on content tab. Article pane is moved at end of window width.\r\n\r\nFollow steps below to repro issue.\r\n\r\n1) Go to content tab.\r\n\r\n![1](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/51179/1382734/43f3c6a0-3b32-11e3-866d-0ec44e6dc949.png)\r\n\r\n2) Minimize browser with till its shown in mobile layout.\r\n\r\n![2](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/51179/1382750/63f858c6-3b32-11e3-847e-b3f804265134.png)\r\n\r\n3) Click on one of article so it will show article with back button/link at top.\r\n\r\n![3](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/51179/1382757/79a0dc5c-3b32-11e3-99eb-81c3ddc7cf6a.png)\r\n\r\n4) Click Maximize button on window so it will take full height and width on screen. It shows only article text and **do not come to original layout.**\r\n\r\n![4](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/51179/1382780/d7ca00d8-3b32-11e3-8d10-5320380446ec.png)\r\n\r\n5) Again reduce width on window and click on back, once it is back to Article list layout, click Maximize button on window so it will take full height and width on screen. **It shows disturbed screen layout.**\r\n\r\n![5](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/51179/1382792/034f99de-3b33-11e3-86b2-6298ad889ac3.png)\r\n\r\n![6](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/51179/1382803/1c3caeb4-3b33-11e3-8d18-ea80bf92aec2.png)\r\n\r\n'
