1159,'','Embedded flash overlaps delete dialog\nIt is not possible to delete a post from the content view when it contains an embedded flash object:\r\n\r\n![](http://i.imgur.com/bJOCgcH.png)\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce:\r\n- Create a new post, paste the code below and save it\r\n\r\n```\r\n<object width="560" height="315"><param name="movie" value="//www.youtube.com/v/n1HChHB0kj0?hl=en_US&amp;version=3"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="//www.youtube.com/v/n1HChHB0kj0?hl=en_US&amp;version=3" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="315" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>\r\n```\r\n\r\n- Go to the content view and click delete on that post\r\n'
