960,'',"Mobile Editing is buggered in iOS 7\nProblems;\r\n\r\n* [ ] Markdown field is impossible to focus, which means no writing.\r\n* [ ] Tag text input is now not sliding up like it used to.\r\n* [ ] Post settings tooltip goes off screen.\r\n\r\nProbably a ton of other shit too.\r\n\r\n![screen shot 2013-10-02 at 10 57 59](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/367517/1252399/41755a90-2b49-11e3-8f19-dead2405c16b.png)\r\n![screen shot 2013-10-02 at 10 58 08](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/367517/1252400/4258ebf2-2b49-11e3-8b32-5f4bcfd56f73.png)\r\n\r\nI'll get working on fixing these asap.\r\n\r\n**Update 1**\r\nThe tag focus problem seems to be a 'clicking' issue, the 'click' listener no longer seems to be registering on the tag toggle element. Changing to a `focus` listener on the input fixes this, but causes other problems.\r\n\r\n**Update 2**\r\nFastClick seems to be causing all the issues relating clicking, this includes the tags not sliding up _and_ the editor not focusing.\r\n"
