903,'',"Usage docs - explanation of environments\nWe need to explain, nicely, about environments. This should be aimed at all the PHP developers who've never experienced this before. What development is, what production is, when to use each one, why and how.\r\n\r\nWorth mentioning ease of deployments, a timelessly tricky task with WP.\r\n\r\nAlso worth a cursory explanation that most folk don't need to worry about testing & Travis - they're for devs."
