815,'matthojo','Usability: Clicking on Post Settings labes does not shift focus to appropriate field\n## Summary of Issue\r\n\r\nThe labels for the Pub Date and Slug post settings fields do not actually tie to their input fields, so tapping/clicking on them does not shift the focus to the corresponding input field.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n 1. Navigate to the content editor via New Post\r\n 2. Click the settings widget in the bottom right hand corner\r\n 3. Tap/click on the Pub Date label\r\n\r\n## Observed Result\r\n\r\nFocus is not shifted to the Pub Date input field.\r\n\r\n## Additional Information\r\n\r\nClient OS: Windows 8 Professional x64\r\nServer OS: Vagrant Box\r\nNode Version: v0.10.5\r\nLatest Commit: f661ad9a63ab3752fb56fefa49544cd472f788b0'
814,'','Published Date appears to be updated every time the field loses focus\n## Summary of Issue\r\n\r\nJust focusing on the published date field in the post settings widget and tabbing off of it triggers a successful update of publish date notification even though the value has not changed.\r\n\r\n**Note:** I believe this is because we are doing a string comparison of the formatted date to the actual ISO date string returned from the DB.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n 1. Navigate to an existing post\r\n 2. Click the settings icon in the bottom right\r\n 3. Click on the Pub Date field\r\n 4. Click outside of the Pub Date field\r\n\r\n## Observed Result\r\n\r\nA success notification is triggered for the pre-existing value\r\n\r\n## Additional Information\r\n\r\nClient OS: Windows 8 Professional x64\r\nServer OS: Vagrant Box\r\nNode Version: v0.10.5\r\nLatest Commit: f661ad9a63ab3752fb56fefa49544cd472f788b0'
813,'','False success notifications on changing password\n## Summary of Issue\r\n\r\nIt is possible to receive a success notification when attempting to change your account password, when in fact the password has **not** been changed.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n 1. Navigate to Settings -> User\r\n 2. Enter an **incorrect** value for "Old Password"\r\n 3. Enter and confirm a new password\r\n 4. Save, note you receive a success notification\r\n 5. Signout\r\n 6. Attempt to log in with the new password, note that you cannot, but that you can signin with your old password\r\n\r\n## Observed Result\r\n\r\nYou receive a success notification when in fact your old password is incorrect.\r\n\r\n## Additional Information\r\n\r\nClient OS: Windows 8 Professional x64\r\nServer OS: Vagrant Box\r\nNode Version: v0.10.5\r\nLatest Commit: f661ad9a63ab3752fb56fefa49544cd472f788b0'
