611,'','Writing post with browser window to narrow disables preview\nSummary of Issue \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nWriting post with browser window to narrow disables preview\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- create a new post\r\n- start writing in post\r\n- make the window narrower\r\n\r\nObserved result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nWhen making the window narrower there is a specific spot where the markdown section covers the preview section and you can no longer see the preview.\r\n\r\n![post with window to small](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/4643742/1068671/0c5f30d4-13f6-11e3-8dd1-fd5826ed25ac.gif)\r\n\r\n\r\nAdditional Information \r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nClient OS: Mac OS X 10.8.4\r\nServer OS: CentOS 6.4\r\nNode Version: 0.10.16\r\nGhost Build Number: 0.2.1\r\nLatest Commit: 13646f9ef6a5ac6100f3b4286e2efabd6a4bf436\r\nBrowser: Chrome 29.0.1547.62'
