600,'','on /ghost/signin/ clicking LOG IN with server stopped shows generic error\nSummary of Issue \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\non /ghost/signin/ clicking LOG IN with server stopped shows generic error\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- sign out of ghost\r\n- stop the server\r\n- click the LOG IN button\r\n\r\nObserved result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nGhost displays this message:\r\n\r\nThe server returned an error (?). \r\n\r\n![screen shot 2013-09-01 at 12 43 40 pm](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/4643742/1064590/804340b4-1340-11e3-905b-e5e0c2b97335.png)\r\n\r\nDesired result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nDisplay some sort useful message\r\n\r\nAdditional Information \r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nClient OS: Mac OS X 10.8.4\r\nServer OS: CentOS 6.4\r\nNode Version: 0.10.16\r\nGhost Build Number: 0.2.1\r\nLatest Commit: d2cafe87b642ca78ac99bd28af1a049673118612\r\nBrowser: Chrome 29.0.1547.57'
599,'','rss feed autodetection\nSummary of Issue \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nfeedly (and assuming all rss readers) can not detect rss feed url from domain name\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- put domain name into rss reader (http://www.ghostqa.com)\r\n- rss reader will fail to detect the rss feed url\r\n\r\n\r\nObserved result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- using feedly I can not just put http://www.ghostqa.com in and have it detect rss feed url\r\n- putting http://www.ghostqa.com/rss/ works\r\n\r\nDesired result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nNeed to make it easier for people to subscribe to the rss feed.  \r\n\r\n- auto detection\r\n- if somebody does type in the domain they MUST type it in with the trailing / (ie must be http://www/ghostqa.com/rss/ and can not be http://www/ghostqa.com/rss)\r\n\r\nAdditional Information \r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nClient OS: Mac OS X 10.8.4\r\nServer OS: CentOS 6.4\r\nNode Version: 0.10.16\r\nGhost Build Number: 0.2.1\r\nLatest Commit: d2cafe87b642ca78ac99bd28af1a049673118612\r\nBrowser: Chrome 29.0.1547.57'
