540,'',"UI: Not obvious how to return to menu in single column responsive view\nIn settings and content pages, it isn't obvious how to return to the menu.\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n* Shrink browser window to ~512px wide. Small. Not too small.\r\n* In the settings area, choose an item (i.e. General.)\r\n* Change your mind. You were really after the profile page! Damn. Why'd you click on that General category then? Silly.\r\n* ...go back? Oh.\r\n\r\n### Suggested remedy\r\n\r\nA more obvious `< back` button, perhaps in the header area (with the section title.)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nImage attached.\r\n\r\n![Missing back button!](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/453993/1025014/c92b5f04-0e37-11e3-8402-7617e46b36cd.png)\r\n"
