453,'','First pass at 404 page\n**Needs Retina screen testing before merge**\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/TryGhost/Ghost/issues/447.\r\n\r\nThis needs Javascript to vertically center the page content. This should be applicable by applying `$(".js-error-container").center();` in the Backbone view, see the login Backbone view for more details.\r\nShould look like;\r\n![screen shot 2013-08-19 at 13 37 01](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/367517/985888/1621a668-08cc-11e3-9a15-5ed7a965c51d.png)\r\n\r\nLooks like;\r\n![screen shot 2013-08-19 at 13 14 19](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/367517/985883/024b3118-08cc-11e3-978d-b660f57e2a39.png)\r\n\r\n**Update**\r\nNew Mobile version (will be vertically centered);\r\n![screen shot 2013-08-19 at 16 34 19](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/367517/987097/05d64d5e-08e5-11e3-9270-4127a65d483e.png)\r\nAlso \'Smushed\' images.\r\n\r\n'
