442,'','Large image gets cut off\nSummary of Issue \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nLarge image gets cut off\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- new post with following in body:\r\n\r\nfirst line of text\r\n\r\n<img src="http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/original/0/2986/954517-ghostbusters_2_slimer_bill_murray_statue_of_libert1.jpg">\r\n\r\nObserved result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- In the markdown preview it scales the image and looks correct\r\n- Viewing the post on the live site results in the right hand side being cut off (see skreenshot)\r\n\r\n![screen shot 2013-08-18 at 5 59 52 pm](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/4643742/983561/0c2701a0-086b-11e3-97ea-70b34aaaf2bd.png)\r\n![screen shot 2013-08-18 at 5 59 57 pm](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/4643742/983562/0c292f48-086b-11e3-8c5b-cef26817d220.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nDesired result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nTo be able to see the whole image\r\n\r\nAdditional Information \r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nClient OS: Mac OS X 10.8.4\r\nServer OS: CentOS 6\r\nNode Version: 0.10.16\r\nGhost Build Number: 0.2.1\r\nLatest Commit: 892adf68d7ac41b8f9aee6a6d0c9dab69378d69f\r\nBrowser: Chrome 28.0.1500.95'
441,'','multi line of html tags gets weird indent\nSummary of Issue \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nmulti line of html tags gets weird indent\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- create new post\r\n- add following text to the body:\r\n\r\n```\r\nnormal text\r\n\r\n<i>this is italic</i>\r\n\r\n<b>bold me</b>\r\n\r\n<u>underline me</u>\r\n```\r\n\r\nObserved result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- first two lines look correct\r\n- 3rd and 4th line are indented\r\n\r\nDesired result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nnone of the lines should be indented\r\n\r\n\r\nAdditional Information \r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nClient OS: Mac OS X 10.8.4\r\nServer OS: CentOS 6\r\nNode Version: 0.10.16\r\nGhost Build Number: 0.2.1\r\nLatest Commit: 892adf68d7ac41b8f9aee6a6d0c9dab69378d69f\r\nBrowser: Chrome 28.0.1500.95'
