416,'','List markdown keyboard shortcut will not allow indented child items\nSummary of Issue \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nList markdown keyboard shortcut will not allow indented child items\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\n- Edit content\r\n- press Ctrl + L and type parent item\r\n- press Ctrl + L and then tab in (to create child item) and type child item\r\n\r\nalso tried\r\n\r\n- Edit content\r\n- press Ctrl + L and type parent item\r\n- tab in and then press Ctrl + L (to create child item) and type child item\r\n\xa0\xa0\r\nObserved result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nboth items are parent level\r\n\xa0\xa0\r\nDesired result \r\n------------------------------- \r\n\r\nusing he keyboard shortcut child items should be possible.  Currently the only way is to type the * manually\r\n\r\n\r\nAdditional Information \r\n-------------------------------\r\n\r\nClient OS: Mac OS X 10.8.4\r\nServer OS: CentOS 6\r\nNode Version: 0.10.16\r\nGhost Build Number: 0.2.1\r\nBrowser: Chrome 28.0.1500.95'
