147,'','User Management UI Front End\nWe need to markup and style the user management screen properly\r\n\r\n94b9fe10998977bad618451b9347136e3207228b needs to be completely refactored. Wrong spacing, not following any CSS code standards, nested too deep, selectors too specific, and needs to actually match the design!\r\n\r\nThese styles should also be moved out of settings.scss and into (new file) users.scss\r\n\r\n![manage users](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/120485/647248/b8b99aa2-d3fc-11e2-85a6-e459ee0853f4.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n'
146,'',"Image Upload: Markdown breaks with special characters in alt text\nPutting any special characters in the alt text of an image - for example a comma, hyphen or apostrophe:\r\n\r\n`!image[My face, no but really - it's my face]`\r\n\r\nCauses the image uploader not to appear."
